	<h2 style="color:lightblue;"> What is AI? </h2>
	<hr>
  <p> AI or also more commonely know as artificial intelligence is a concept is technology that uses computing power to
    formulate intelligence the can compute a task or algorithm on its own. The many concepts of AI can cover more serious
    deeper issues relating to the consequenece if a sentient AI is to develop or if some other drawback were to ouccer.
    AI has helped humanity in many tasks in lifes that needed computing power to get a task done more efficently or to
    furhur the cause of technology. None the less AI is a controversial topic that must be looked into in furthur detail.
  </p>
	<p> the concepts of AI and how it can be beneficial or disastrious for humanity</p>
    <li> furthur tech progress </li>
    <li> potentially make humanity more advance (ideal scenairo)</li>
    <li> may destroy humanity </li>
    <li> may be evil </li>
